HEADWORD: Ironweed
<hw>I"ron*weed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A tall weed with purplish flowers (<spn>Vernonia
Noveboracensis</spn>). The name is also applied to other plants of the
same genus.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ironwood</ent>⟦br⟧
